{
  "stem": "12768.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The committee came-- you, you made the raw material halfway finished.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then they came and they stamped it with a deep stamp in them so that you couldn't cheat when you had to finish the instrument.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I made my own lenses for the optical instrument.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In those days we ground our own lenses.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The cross-hair was used on lenses in those days were black widow spider cocoons.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And you unrolled them until the spider, you know-- and that was put across a lens as a cross-hair.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I finished with a, with a nice mention on my certificate of, of master mechanic now, or instrument maker, as it was called.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Of course, that became a good thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because in the United States, that became a, a very nice and noble trade.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so we had a funny incidence.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I mean, we went to our summer town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we enjoyed going back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And my two friends that lived there during the war time, the Mattsen, had now moved to another city in Denmark.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I will tell you how I met one of them later on, you know, and almost 50 years later.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And in 1949, I had family in New York.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "My uncle and aunt, Max Itkin and Elsa Itkin and their son Charlie, had gone to the World's Fair in 1939.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they came on the shame ship as now Victor Borge, that time Borge Rosenbaum.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Came to United States, to the World's Fair.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And, of course, the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Now they couldn't go back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Borge Rosenbaum became Victor Borge, because he got a recording contract with the Victor Recording Company.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said, your name is too long, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
